      vs ../acl/x_[scope]_case_party_read_agent_assigned.xml (agent READ
      assigned-only on case_party):
        - <roles>         x_[scope]_case_manager
                                            vs x_[scope]_case_agent
        - <advanced>      false             vs true (the agent ACL carries
                                              a scripted condition that
                                              dereferences current.case to
                                              apply the parent-case
                                              "Assigned only" predicate;
                                              the manager ACL is
                                              unconditional)
        - <condition>     empty             vs encoded query that asserts
